p: The dataset contained 28,671 laboratory-confirmed cases of RSV; 18,451 cases of influenza A; 4767 cases of influenza B; 1347 cases of Enterovirus; 4945 cases of metapneumovirus; and 31,281 cases of rhinovirus over 13 years (total = 89,462). (See Figure 2 for raw frequency plot of all viruses. See Table A1 for frequency data of each virus in each seasonal year.)
